## 3. Investment Pathway Optimization
UIOS autonomously identifies the highest-value pathways for investment by evaluating:

- long-range payoff  
- compound ecosystem benefit  
- risk-adjusted impact  
- technological maturity  
- cross-company synergy  
- acceleration of mission-critical timelines  

Example:  
An investment in Optimus propagates ROI to Tesla factories, Starlink installation teams, SpaceX manufacturing, and Neuralink clean rooms simultaneously.

